模块 com.ae2dms.bubblebobble
程序包 com.ae2dms.bubblebobble.model

类 GameObject

java.lang.Object
com.ae2dms.bubblebobble.model.GameObject
直接已知子类:
MovableObject, UnmovableObject
public abstract class GameObject extends Object
GameObjects are the objects on the InteractableWorld screen. Movable GameObject has a velocity, acceleration, position, direction, and dimensions. While unmovable GameObject don not have. GameObjects can detect if they are overlapping another GameObject and must implement methods of collisions with every type of Unit.
